You are helping build a Local Magik "Magik Button" in this folder. A button is config — a single
button.json (questions to ask + ordered steps to run), not code.

Read AGENTS.md (the workflow) and FORMAT.md (the full button.json field reference) in this folder,
then create/edit button.json accordingly and use the CLI:
  npm run validate    # schema + graph checks
  npm run dry-run     # offline preview (stub AI, no sends)
  npm run publish     # stage it as a Draft — user clicks Go live in Build (add --live to skip staging)

Keep to one clear job per button; re-run validate after every edit to button.json.
